.header Are you sure?
.content
	p Are you sure you want to delete the instance #[strong #{name}]? This action is irreversable.
	.ui.checkbox
		input(type="checkbox" name="deleteFolder" checked)
		label(style="color: white;") Delete the instance folder. #[strong IMPORTANT:] This will delete all your worlds and other resources in this instance.
.actions
	.ui.button.cancel.inverted.basic.blue Cancel
	.ui.button.approve.inverted.red Delete it
